These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, soy-milk, lemonade
4 different pets are kept: ferret, bird, hamster, frog
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, trike, taxi, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the ferret##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
7. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | juice  | lemonade | soy-milk    | hot-chocolate       |
| Pet         | bird | frog    | hamster      | ferret |
| Transport   | helicopter   | taxi | trike | airplane        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, kiwi, artichoke, pomegranate
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, teacher, pilot, electrician
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, trike, subway, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the electrician##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the pilot is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is the security-guard##1
6. the person driving the boat is the person eating kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | artichoke   | kiwi | orange     | pomegranate      |
| Job         | teacher | pilot | electrician | security-guard |
| Transport   | trike    | boat   | subway     | helicopter      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, filmmaking, cooking, dancing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, punk, blues, rock
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, british, italian, nigerian
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the british is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the fan of rock is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan of blues##1
5. the nigerian is on the right of the fan of punk##1
6. the nigerian is on the right of the italian##1
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku | filmmaking | cooking | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | punk    | salsa | blues     |
| Nationality   | dutch | italian    | nigerian | british    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, musician, mechanic, photographer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, badminton, surfing, climbing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, ship, snowmobile, helicopter
1. the mechanic is the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the musician is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the mechanic##1
7. the mechanic is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
8. the photographer is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | journalist | photographer | mechanic | musician |
| Sport       | badminton     | climbing      | lacrosse     | surfing      |
| Transport   | ship | bus         | helicopter      | snowmobile        |

