.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, skydiving, fishing, card-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, disaster, documentary, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, baseball, water-polo, basketball
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | fishing   | card-games | skydiving  | hiking      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | musical        | martial-arts  | disaster       |
| Sport         | cycling | water-polo    | baseball | basketball |

