3. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the photographer##1
4. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
5. the teacher is on the far left##1
6. the person watching drama movies is the firefighter##1
7. the fan of house is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
8. the photographer is the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | teacher | firefighter | photographer | journalist |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | drama  | martial-arts | romance   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | r&b     | gospel | house       |

