.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, zucchini, lime, lettuce
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, writing, traveling, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, superhero, satire, action
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is the person eating lime##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
8. the person who's hobby is writing is the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food          | strawberry  | lettuce | lime   | zucchini     |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | writing   | rock-climbing  | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | satire         | time-travel  | superhero | action  |

