.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, coffee, sprite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, thriller, horror, documentary
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, russian, indian, australian
1. the person drinking cola is the indian##1
2. the australian is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the indian##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
6. the australian is the person drinking coffee##1
7. the russian is on the left of the australian##1
8. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | sprite | coffee     | hot-chocolate | cola |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | satire | horror       | thriller    |
| Nationality   | russian   | australian | dutch    | indian |

