.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, radish, artichoke, apple
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, techno, metal, country
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, basketball, skiing, sailing
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the person eating apple##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of metal##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is the person eating radish##1
5. the person eating radish is on the right of the fan of country##1
6. the fan of country is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | artichoke        | apple   | radish  | lime   |
| Music-Genre   | funk         | country     | techno    | metal       |
| Sport         | basketball | surfing | skiing | sailing |

