.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, sprite, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: kale, cucumber, apricot, papaya
4 different pets are kept: frog, ferret, lizard, hedgehog
1. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the person eating kale is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | sprite | lemonade | juice        |
| Food       | papaya | kale  | cucumber | apricot     |
| Pet        | ferret    | lizard   | hedgehog  | frog |

