.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, lawyer, teacher, nurse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, surfing, swimming, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, snowmobile, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the lawyer##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the nurse##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person driving the jet-ski##1
8. the person who's sport is swimming is the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | writer  | nurse | lawyer  | teacher |
| Sport       | swimming | surfing        | tennis | rowing       |
| Transport   | motorbike   | snowmobile          | taxi          | jet-ski       |

