1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the british is on the left of the nigerian##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is the indonesian##1
7. the british is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
