.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: classical-climbing, sudoku, filmmaking, collecting
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, indie, classical, country
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, cycling, soccer, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the fan of country##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the fan of country##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the fan of indie##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the fan of disco##1
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's hobby is classical-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | collecting | sudoku    | classical-climbing        | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | indie     | classical     | country        | disco   |
| Sport         | cycling   | parkour | soccer | tennis  |

