3. the italian is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the french##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
7. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
8. the brazilian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports   | disaster  | family    | romance    |
| Nationality   | chinese | french  | italian  | brazilian |
| Transport     | jet-ski  | scooter | taxi | bike        |

