The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, spy, musical, disaster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, ice-hockey, skiing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is the person drinking cola##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the person drinking milk is the person watching animation movies##1
8. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
