4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the japanese is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | australian | indian | japanese | pakistani |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | biathlon | skiing  | baseball  |
| Transport     | bus  | taxi | ship     | trike  |

