3. the firefighter is on the right of the mechanic##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the police-officer##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby       | filmmaking | cooking | singing | drawing |
| Job         | police-officer | entrepreneur  | mechanic   | firefighter      |
| Transport   | skateboard        | quad-bike  | subway   | train         |

