.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, mechanic, analyst, lawyer
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, indian, british
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, sailing, basketball, cricket
1. the mechanic is on the left of the american##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
4. the indian is on the far right##1
5. the american is the person who's sport is basketball##1
6. the british is on the far left##1
7. the lawyer is on the far right##1
8. the british is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | mechanic  | analyst  | videographer | lawyer |
| Nationality   | british   | american | japanese   | indian      |
| Sport         | skiing | basketball    | sailing   | cricket         |

 